node.title: Fisherman dead in Bay of Plenty after being swept out to sea crossing river
node.content: ["A person fishing at a river mouth near a Bay of Plenty settlement has been found dead after being swept out to sea.", "According to police, officers were notified at 8:30pm on Wednesday that a person could be in difficulty in the sea near State Highway 35, Omaio.", "They are thought to have been fishing near a river mouth and swept out to sea while attempting to cross the river.", "Police say an extensive search was undertaken and the person was found dead overnight.", "\"Police would like to thank all those who assisted in the search, including residents from the local community,\" a spokesperson said.", "\"Police will make enquiries into the death on behalf of the Coroner.\""]
